OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy
OL,6,Fperiods with showers dying out to
OL,7,Fstart the evening, soon becoming
OL,8,Fgenerally dry with clear spells and
OL,9,Fthe wind easing. Cloud thickening
OL,10,Fovernight however, with rain arriving
OL,11,Fbefore dawn.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FCloudy and damp start with
OL,14,Fthe wind increasing. Rain will
OL,15,Fpossibly be heavy in the morning,
OL,16,Fbecoming confined to western parts in
OL,17,Fthe afternoon. Brighter spells later
OL,18,Fin the east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
